ern support. According to Qassem, Hezbollah's resistance forced Israeli Pri=
me Minister Benjamin Netanyahu to accept the ceasefire. Shortly after the 2=
006 war, some Hezbollah fighters claimed to have seen the Mahdi striking Is=
